title: United Kingdom Imports - Misc. Manufactured Articles (Breakdown By Comm. Code)
description: Imports - Misc. Manufactured Articles (Breakdown By Comm. Code) in the United Kingdom increased to 150.20 GBP Million in September from 149.05 GBP Million in August of 2022. Manufactured Articles (Breakdown B in the United Kingdom averaged 91.03 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 179.93 GBP Million in October of 2019 and a record low of 39.57 GBP Million in February of 2000.
